Title: 010: Model Validation, Data Exhaust and Organisational Cultural Change with Yaw Tan
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Senior Data Scientist Yaw Tan. You will learn about model validation and a lot more about modelling, get to know about the power of data exhaust and hear some thoughts about cultural change in organisations.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at https://www.superdatascience.com/10
